The church released an official response to the musical, stating: 'The production may attempt to entertain audiences for an evening, but the Book of Mormon as a volume of scripture will change people's lives forever by bringing them closer to Christ.'

Matt Stone, one of the show's creators, described The Book of Mormon as 'an atheist's love letter to religion'.

Earlier in the day the Prime Minister was at the EU summit in Brussels.

